      "content": "rebuilding? how? there is nothing to rebuild from. the debt is in my name, the reputation is gone, i've ruined everything we worked for for ten years. it's not just a bad decision, it's who i am now. a loser. a fraud. there's no \"trying\" your way out of this kind of debt and shame. it's just a permanent stain. everything i touch just breaks.",
